          <article class="project card" data-category="data api" tabindex="0"
            data-title="Assignment: EV Battery Health Dashboard"
			data-desc="Data-focused assignment exploring how battery health metrics could be visualized for electric vehicles. Designed dashboard layouts to represent charging cycles, efficiency trends, and battery degradation concepts."
